- @page_title = "Xero"


%section#pagetitle
  .uk-container.uk-container-center
    .uk-grid
      .uk-width-1-1.uk-width-small-1-1
        %h3 Add-ons: Xero Accounting
%section.uk-padding.uk-margin-top
  .uk-container.uk-container-center
    %h2 Dive Centre HQ is a one-stop software solution for dive stores
    .uk-text-large It is a simple, intuitive and easy to use sales, event and crm tool for dive stores. It's online and suited to small businesses in the dive industry.
    = image_tag 'dchq-xero.jpg'
    %hr.uk-margin-large-top
    .uk-grid
      .uk-width-2-10.uk-width-medium-2-10.uk-hidden-small
        .icon-wrap.center.idz-bottom-adjustment5
          = image_tag 'xero-add-on-partner-logo.jpg'
      .uk-width-8-10.uk-width-medium-8-10.uk-width-small-1-1
        %h2.uk-text-thin.uk-margin-medium-top
          Connect
          %strong Dive Centre HQ and Xero
          for a total business solution
        .uk-grid.uk-margin-medium-top
          .uk-width-4-10
            %p Dive Centre HQ further improves the workflow fo dealing with all your sales data by integrating with Xero - beautiful accounting software. Connect the apps today and see a noticeable different in time spent on your accounts.
          .uk-width-3-10
            %ul
              %li Xero displays your realtime cash balances - compare live data to your recent acquisition costs.
              %li Sales invoices paid in Dive Centre HQ are automatically imported into Xero.
          .uk-width-3-10
            %ul
              %li Sales records are cleverly matched to your customer records in Xero.
              %li Choose between batch processing or individual records being pushed to Xero.

    %hr.uk-margin-large-top.uk-margin-large-bottom
    .uk-grid
      .uk-width-1-1
        %h4 What is Xero?
        %p Xero is easy to use online accounting software that’s designed specifically for small businesses.
        %ul
          %li It's all online, so you can work when and where you want to. Just login with your PC, Mac or mobile.
          %li Your bank statements are automatically imported and categorized, letting you see your cashflow in real­time.
          %li Invite your team and work together on financials. You can collaborate over your up­to­date numbers.
          %li Xero has all you need to run your business – including invoicing, paying bills, sales tax returns, reporting and much more.
        %p
          Find out more or try
          = link_to 'Xero Accounting Software', 'http://www.xero.com'
          for free.


    .uk-panel-box.idz-panel.green.uk-margin-medium-top
      .uk-grid.uk-text-contrast
        .uk-width-1-1
          %h2.uk-margin-small-bottom.uk-text-contrast
            Connect Xero to Dive Centre HQ
          %p.uk-text-large.uk-margin-top-remove.idz-tablet-landscape-hidden Login to DCHQ and go to Add-ons. Follow the step-by-step process to connect to Xero.
